profile:
Your home comfort is our priority.

--

24-HOUR EMERGENCY SERVICE
365 DAYS A YEAR
1-866-260-0023

--

3 OFFICES TO SERVE YOU BETTER: NEWMARKET, OSHAWA, and ORILLIA!

--

Comfort Masters Ltd. is an experienced, reliable, and courteous home comfort company with offices in Newmarket, Orillia and Oshawa. We are factory, industry, and provincially trained, and fully insured. We take care of all of your home comfort needs, specializing in heating and cooling, and indoor air quality.

We treat every job as if it was being preformed in our own home. We stand behind all of the products we sell, and all of the installs we preform. We make sure every job is completed properly the first time around, however we are always there to answer our clients questions whenever they may arise.

We are your one stop shop for all of your Home Comfort needs. 

--

Servicing: Toronto, GTA, Stouffville, Markham, Newmarket, Georgina, Pickering, Ajax, Whitby, Oshawa, Bowmanville, Georgina, Caledon, Nobleton, Aurora, Uxbridge, King City, Vaughan, Mount Albert, Richmond Hill, Goodwood, Barrie, Orillia, Durham Region.
--
Services: Heating, cooling, furnace, gas fireplace, electric fireplace, air conditioner, A/C, central air, indoor air quality, boiler, hot water tank, tankless water heater, duct cleaning, plumbing, water filtration, water purification, ductless air conditioner, heat pump, custom duct work, humidifier, thermostats, HRV, ERV, hepa filter, indoor air quality, filters, gas line installation, in floor heating, electronic air cleaner, gas stove, service, maintenance, repair, fix furnace, alarm systems, alarms, burglar alarms, residential, commercial.
